- That's up to your brother.

32
00:10:18,847 --> 00:10:22,123
Colmar, military airport.

33
00:12:06,567 --> 00:12:08,000
Secured.

34
00:12:21,607 --> 00:12:24,997
Northeast-Albania

35
00:12:32,247 --> 00:12:35,637
