the German, Italian and French police.

49
00:18:13,727 --> 00:18:16,878
The trial being held in Strasbourg
has a symbolic meaning.

50
00:18:22,447 --> 00:18:25,280
Strasbourg - Industrial Park

51
00:18:39,887 --> 00:18:41,878
Are you scared?

52
00:18:44,807 --> 00:18:49,119
Who do you think you are?
You're the woman here.

53
00:18:49,247 --> 00:18:52,319
You can sit in front of the computer,
that's it.

54
00:18:52,447 --> 00:18:55,325
And if you're nice, who knows...

55
00:18:55,447 --> 00:19:00,157
Selim, don't even think about it.
I don't like you.

56
00:19:16,847 --> 00:19:18,678
Go on, Martial.

57
00:19:31,287 --> 00:19:34,882
Slavery is the right word.

58
