- He's tied up.

87
00:30:13,527 --> 00:30:15,677
Quiet. Get up.

88
00:30:19,887 --> 00:30:23,482
Don't move.
- Take my gun.

89
00:30:25,607 --> 00:30:27,757
Take it.

90
00:30:28,607 --> 00:30:30,882
