- We're no heroes.

93
00:30:55,727 --> 00:30:59,515
Everything alright?
Did you tie them up well?

94
00:30:59,647 --> 00:31:03,640
Martial was good, eh?
What an acrobat.

95
00:31:03,767 --> 00:31:08,682
Go stand on the lookout.
Now you can prove yourself.

96
00:32:01,767 --> 00:32:03,325
Roadwork?

97
