233
01:03:07,167 --> 01:03:10,284
Haven't you got anything else for me?

234
01:03:15,087 --> 01:03:17,885
Shut up.
- Stupid bitch.

235
01:03:27,687 --> 01:03:29,837
What are you doing?

236
01:03:31,167 --> 01:03:33,727
We're all in the same shit.

237
01:03:59,687 --> 01:04:02,121
Hey, you there.

238
01:04:02,247 --> 01:04:05,364
Come down and get this on.

239
01:04:06,367 --> 01:04:08,642
Have you got any weapons?
- A short rifle.

240
01:04:08,767 --> 01:04:10,962
Get him.

241
01:04:26,007 --> 01:04:28,282
Don't shoot. I'm the security guard.

242
01:04:28,407 --> 01:04:30,796
Do you have a gun?
- No.

243
01:04:36,207 --> 01:04:38,880
Take it.
- I'm not a part of this.

244
01:04:39,007 --> 01:04:42,158
I have to watch my screens.

245
01:04:43,207 --> 01:04:45,767
What's your name?
- Spitz.

246
01:04:47,767 --> 01:04:51,043
Make yourself useful, Spitz,
and put on this vest.

247
01:04:51,167 --> 01:04:54,716
