251
01:06:25,247 --> 01:06:27,078
Turn.

252
01:06:30,287 --> 01:06:32,005
Lower, lower.

253
01:06:33,007 --> 01:06:35,567
Managing?
- Let it go.

254
01:08:35,367 --> 01:08:38,518
