- Gone for help.

255
01:08:43,647 --> 01:08:45,638
Hang in there.

256
01:08:45,767 --> 01:08:49,396
Don't worry,
we'll be lying in the sun soon.

257
01:09:07,247 --> 01:09:08,999
What's that?

258
01:09:11,727 --> 01:09:14,002
Don't be foolish. Come back.

259
01:09:16,047 --> 01:09:20,438
Come back, Spitz.
- Don't shoot. I surrender.

260
01:09:20,567 --> 01:09:22,762
I surrender.

261
01:09:22,887 --> 01:09:24,684
Don't shoot.

262
01:10:08,927 --> 01:10:10,679
Get out, bastard.

263
01:10:18,247 --> 01:10:21,000
Out of the way
- Put him back right now.

264
01:10:27,127 --> 01:10:30,005
Lower those weapons.

265
01:10:34,887 --> 01:10:37,685
They can have their leader.
This has to stop.

266
01:10:37,807 --> 01:10:40,162
Get back.
- Shut up.

267
01:10:40,287 --> 01:10:43,279
Get out of the way
or I'll shoot him.

268
01:10:43,407 --> 01:10:48,959
Do you know who that asshole is?
He raped hundreds of women.

269
01:10:49,087 --> 01:10:51,647
I don't give a damn.

270
01:10:52,647 --> 01:10:54,239
Is that clear?

271
01:10:55,767 --> 01:10:59,999
You don't understand, Selim.
That guy stays here.

272
01:11:00,127 --> 01:11:03,278
Put him back.
- What's wrong with you?

273
01:11:03,407 --> 01:11:05,318
Back.

274
01:11:40,607 --> 01:11:42,802
What's in there?

275
01:11:44,887 --> 01:11:46,798
Goddamned.

276
01:12:22,727 --> 01:12:24,399
Let go.

277
01:14:22,407 --> 01:14:24,716
Is that your kid?

278
01:14:28,007 --> 01:14:31,363
A cute one. How old is he?

279
01:14:31,487 --> 01:14:33,603
Exactly one year.

280
01:14:35,007 --> 01:14:39,683
I have a son too.
My mother looks after him.

281
01:14:39,807 --> 01:14:42,685
How old is he?
- Six.

282
01:14:42,807 --> 01:14:45,560
A big one.

283
01:14:45,687 --> 01:14:47,996
And his dad?

284
01:14:53,407 --> 01:14:57,161
I wanted to do it on my own.
- I didn't.

285
01:15:08,767 --> 01:15:10,166
No.

286
01:15:20,287 --> 01:15:23,120
Northeast. Movement at ten o'clock.

287
01:15:23,847 --> 01:15:26,315
Southeast. Movement at nine o'clock.

288
01:15:27,487 --> 01:15:30,399
Movement at three o'clock.
- And at five o'clock.

289
01:15:31,407 --> 01:15:35,002
Shit, we'll never make it.

290
01:15:43,487 --> 01:15:46,797
They're regrouping.
- They're going to slaughter us.

291
01:15:48,127 --> 01:15:52,200
They're coming in either way.
- We must buy some time.

292
01:15:52,327 --> 01:15:55,763
If we take cover here,
we can overlook everything.

293
01:15:55,887 --> 01:15:58,117
Not enough cover.

294
01:15:58,247 --> 01:16:00,283
But what else?

295
01:16:02,927 --> 01:16:04,997
I don't know.

296
01:16:09,167 --> 01:16:13,843
We'll build a wall of containers.
Bullets won't go through it.

297
01:16:13,967 --> 01:16:17,755
With loopholes.
- We're building a container wall.

298
01:16:17,887 --> 01:16:22,324
All exits have to be sealed.
That will stop them for a while.

299
01:16:22,447 --> 01:16:25,405
How much ammo do we have left?
- Ten magazines.

300
01:16:25,527 --> 01:16:28,325
I've got two.
- One box of shells.

301
01:16:28,447 --> 01:16:31,484
I've got eight bullets.

302
01:16:31,607 --> 01:16:33,677
That's not much.

303
01:16:37,127 --> 01:16:39,516
Shall we do it?

304
01:16:39,647 --> 01:16:41,239
You stay here.

305
01:16:56,807 --> 01:17:00,322
I have a plan to buy us some time
and get help.

306
01:17:01,327 --> 01:17:03,921
What is it?
- I'll escape.

307
01:17:04,047 --> 01:17:08,359
I know what I'm doing.
You'll just have to trust me.

308
01:17:10,847 --> 01:17:12,724
I'm coming with you.

309
01:17:21,127 --> 01:17:25,564
We haven't got enough chains.
Take that forklift truck.

310
01:17:27,487 --> 01:17:29,159
To the right.

311
01:17:31,087 --> 01:17:34,602
I'm coming back for you, Nasser.
I swear.

312
01:17:34,727 --> 01:17:37,002
With an ambulance.

313
01:17:37,127 --> 01:17:39,925
You know, Selim...

314
01:17:40,047 --> 01:17:43,756
You handled it alright.
I blew it.

315
01:17:43,887 --> 01:17:45,957
No you didn't.

316
01:18:01,327 --> 01:18:03,761
Take good care of her.

317
01:18:35,207 --> 01:18:37,675
We're counting on you.

318
01:18:42,687 --> 01:18:44,439
I'll be fine.

319
01:18:44,567 --> 01:18:46,797
Good luck.

320
01:18:53,167 --> 01:18:54,725
Drive.

321
01:20:03,767 --> 01:20:07,203
Connect, come on connect.

322
01:20:24,447 --> 01:20:29,202
It won't stop, damned.

323
01:20:29,327 --> 01:20:32,524
Calm down.
- I want to go home.

324
01:20:36,807 --> 01:20:40,038
It's my fault, my fault.

325
01:21:03,887 --> 01:21:07,197
I'm staying here
to guard that motherfucker.

326
01:21:42,607 --> 01:21:45,804
Slut.
- No you're the slut.

327
01:21:47,287 --> 01:21:50,199
When I was a little girl...

328
01:21:50,327 --> 01:21:53,000
... a dog like you beat me...

329
01:21:53,127 --> 01:21:55,687
... and dumped his seed in me.

330
01:21:55,807 --> 01:21:59,197
I have sworn
I would crack his balls some day.

331
01:22:04,567 --> 01:22:06,797
What are you doing?

332
01:22:06,927 --> 01:22:10,237
You're hurting me. Stop it.

333
01:22:10,367 --> 01:22:13,484
That's no use. Get lost.

334
01:27:44,887 --> 01:27:46,366
Down there.

335
01:27:58,887 --> 01:28:01,560
Come one.
- I'm staying with him.

336
01:28:01,687 --> 01:28:04,918
You have to go with them.
- No.

337
01:28:10,927 --> 01:28:14,886
The cellar is our only chance.
- Leave a weapon behind.

338
01:28:19,087 --> 01:28:21,123
Four bullets.
- Come on.

339
01:28:22,127 --> 01:28:23,799
Get out of here.

340
01:28:29,527 --> 01:28:31,245
Nasser...

341
01:28:31,767 --> 01:28:35,282
Go on, Santi. Go on.

342
01:28:45,087 --> 01:28:48,159
I'm dying.

343
01:28:48,287 --> 01:28:51,245
You won't leave, will you?

344
01:28:51,367 --> 01:28:53,597
Nonsense, you're not dying.

345
01:28:54,607 --> 01:28:56,518
Let's go.

346
01:29:12,247 --> 01:29:14,442
We're all going to die.

347
01:29:36,287 --> 01:29:38,642
The sun, brother.

348
01:29:41,287 --> 01:29:42,561
The sun...

349
01:29:54,727 --> 01:29:56,160
Turn around.

350
01:30:06,287 --> 01:30:07,686
Come.

351
01:30:11,007 --> 01:30:12,884
Make sure it's spread everywhere.

352
01:30:20,967 --> 01:30:22,446
They're coming.

353
01:30:23,447 --> 01:30:24,960
Inside.

354
01:30:27,447 --> 01:30:29,438
But what about you?

355
01:30:29,567 --> 01:30:31,558
I'll be fine.

356
01:30:33,687 --> 01:30:35,279
I'll be fine.

357
01:33:04,647 --> 01:33:07,639
Beat it.
This is a secured area.

358
01:33:10,407 --> 01:33:13,399
It's an inferno, bodies everywhere.

359
01:33:13,527 --> 01:33:16,200
Are there any survivors?

360
01:33:16,327 --> 01:33:19,080
Get out of here, son. It's too dangerous.

361
01:34:18,407 --> 01:34:22,116
Captain?
Some survivors have been found.

362
01:34:41,167 --> 01:34:43,044
Go away.
